General.Name: TalkPool AG
General.Description: TalkPool AG provides network design, engineering, implementation, and managed services to telecommunications operators, system vendors, and prime contractors. The company offers network planning, remote site management, and documentation services; implementation, operation, and maintenance services; repair and refurbishing services; and camouflage solutions. It also provides professional services and solutions comprising a range of design, creation, and realization of IoT solutions and products. The company serves real estate, construction, insurance, and meter manufacturing and integrator companies. It operates in Europe, America, the Middle East, and Africa. TalkPool AG was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Chur, Switzerland.
